<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/343001ABHMRLTSKCJKLSCGGPTVVHKKCGL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "48 Hour Film Project Screening Night & Best-Of Awards";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/36d24dd0-ef31-4209-8519-1902ffeb5223.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>48 Hour Film Project</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SCREENING & BEST-OF AWARDS</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Unrated films - Viewer discretion advised.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for the 4th Annual 48 Hour Film Project – Okanagan Screening & Awards Night.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It's a celebration of local filmmaking talent and creative chaos.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Over one adrenaline-fueled weekend, teams wrote, shot, edited, and delivered original short films in just 48 hours. Now it’s time to see the results on the big screen and celebrate the standout achievements of this year’s competition.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The evening includes:<span><br/></span>🎬 Screening of all 2026 48 Hour Film Project Okanagan films<span><br/></span>🏆 Best Of Awards Ceremony<span><br/></span>🎉 Community celebration with filmmakers, cast, crew, and film fans<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you participated or just love independent film, come support local creators and experience what can be made in just two days.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $22.61</span>  ($17.30 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.95 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">48 Hour Film Project</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
