<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360201ARKDLVNMRPDGSMVMVQHBRTVJNSM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Alan Doyle Touchdown Kickoff Concert";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/0066ff9e-71bf-48c2-a5f4-787c284caac0.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>BCLC presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">ALAN DOYLE</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><h2>TOUCHDOWN KELOWNA KICKOFF CONCERT</h2><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">with special guests Under the Rocks</span></h2><span><br/></span>Get ready to sing along and kick things off with <span class=\"BoldText\">Alan Doyle,</span> an iconic Canadian performer known for his infectious energy and crowd-pleasing hits and special guests, bluegrass band <span class=\"BoldText\">Under the Rocks.</span> It’s the perfect way to launch a weekend of celebration.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Let’s kick off Touchdown Kelowna’s opening weekend with a high-energy headline performance built for big crowds and bigger moments. We’ve got the sunshine, we’ve got the scenery… now all we need is a proper kitchen party. <span class=\"BoldText\">Alan Doyle</span> is bringing exactly that to kick things off in style.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s your Kickoff Concert - and they’re going to raise the roof, the tent, and maybe a glass or two while they’re at it.  So bring your friends, bring your voices - and they’ll bring the songs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional Information:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li> <span class=\"BoldText\">All‑ages outdoor concert</span></li><li> <span class=\"BoldText\">Gates open:</span> 7 pm</li><li> <span class=\"BoldText\">Seating:</span> General admission lawn (bring a chair or blanket)</li><li> <span class=\"BoldText\">Accessible tickets</span> include one required Support Person access </li><li> <span class=\"BoldText\">Amenities:</span> Food trucks, bar service, full site liquor license</li><li> <span class=\"BoldText\">Location:</span> Waterfront Park Festival Site, Kelowna</li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Concert Bundle Offer:</span><span><br/></span>Attending both headline shows? Purchase tickets to the Kickoff Concert featuring Alan Doyle and Boots on the Beach with The Road Hammers to receive a discounted bundle rate automatically at checkout.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Alan Doyle:</span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://alandoyle.ca/\">alandoyle.ca</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Under the Rocks:</span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.undertherocksband.com/\">undertherocksband.com</a><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><ul><li><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP Admission*  $144.90</span>  ($126.00 base price + $18.90 service charge)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">General Admission  $72.45</span>  ($63.00 base price + $9.45 service charge)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Children 12 and under - General Admission  $50.72</span>  ($44.10.00 base price + $6.62 service charge)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Children 5 and under - General Admission are free</span></li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Concert Bundle Offer:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li>General Admission Kickoff + General Admission Boots on the Beach = <span class=\"BoldText\">$21.00 savings</span></li><li>VIP* Kickoff + VIP* Boots on the Beach = <span class=\"BoldText\">$42.00 savings</span></li><li><span class=\"ItalicText\">Ticket types must match. Discount applies automatically at checkout, no promo code needed.</span></li></ul><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">*VIP Tickets include special VIP area with a private bar and washrooms.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Accessible ticket holders:</span> we request you email theboxoffice@kelowna.ca indicating your accessibility needs and if you will have a Support Person added to your account profile.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The event will proceed rain or shine.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Tickets for <span class=\"BoldText\">Alan Doyle Touchdown Kickoff Concert</span> and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
