<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/378001ASKCGLGPCVNSJNVJVVGRQNBBKTJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Bee Gees Revisited - The Tribute Show";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/af0238bb-f3ef-47db-ae76-656a41be0f9d.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>VaughnCo Entertainment presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">BEE GEES REVISITED</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The Tribute Show</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>VaughnCo Entertainment is proud to present the most outstanding Bee Gees Tribute show. Bee Gees Revisited is the ultimate tribute to the Bee Gees. Come and experience the sound, the harmonies, and the beautiful falsetto voices of the brothers Gibb. Performing with a full band the show recreates the Bee Gees 1998 Las Vegas appearance live.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The costumes, the music, and the atmosphere is as close to the real thing as you can get. The show suspends belief as it weaves through hit after hit from their classic 60’s catalogue to the groove of their 70’s Disco era hits that made the band a world-wide sensation. Dance and sing along to hits like Staying Alive, Night Fever, Massachusetts, Tragedy, You Should Be Dancing, and Nights on Broadway.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All performed note for note by award winning vocalists Colum Henry, Dave Lafame, and Aaron Solomon. This international touring act has played to sold out, standing ovation audiences throughout North America. So put on your white suits, sequence dresses, boogie shoes and get ready to sing and dance the night away with Bee Gees Revisited.  If you are a Bee Gees fan this show is a must see!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $65.15</span>  ($54.60 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.19 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Bee Gees Revisited - The Tribute Show</span> ticket fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
