<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/359401APHBNRQDCQDJPHMMSKHQRLQNVQQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Big Shiny Tunes Kelowna 2pm Show";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/6e7b93c7-1867-47a3-9918-18ed738c722e.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Wentworth Music presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">BIG SHINY TUNES KELOWNA (2pm show)</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Wentworth Music is proud to present - Big Shiny Tunes Kelowna! <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">1 Day - 2 Separate Shows - 30 Total Songs</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">(For the best musical experience buy a 2 show package and make a whole day out of it!)</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Come out and support the future of music here in Kelowna as our best and brightest will perform 2 completely different shows Friday June 26th at the Kelowna Community Theatre! Please be sure to get tickets to the correct show your child will be apart of and cheer all the kids on as they perform some of the best Alternative Rock songs from the 80's Late 90's and early 00's. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Important:</span></span> <span class=\"ItalicText\">The two shows on this date are separate events with different content. Please ensure you are selecting tickets for your intended performance.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">2PM SHOW SETLIST</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><ul><li>GEL - Collective Soul</li><li>WALKIN' ON THE SUN - Smash Mouth</li><li>HUNGRY LIKE THE WOLF - Duran Duran</li><li>LIFE - Our Lady Peace</li><li>CALL ME - Blondie</li><li>IRIS - Goo Goo Dolls</li><li>VIDEO KILLED THE RADIO STAR - The Buggles</li><li>NO RAIN - Blind Melon</li><li>LOVEFOOL - The Cardigans</li><li>IN MY PLACE - Coldplay</li><li>CHANGE (IN THE HOUSE OF FLIES) - Deftones</li><li>MACHINEHEAD - Bush</li><li>SWEETNESS - Jimmy Eat World</li><li>GO WITH THE FLOW - Queens of the Stone Age</li></ul><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $32.55</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.94 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Purchase an equal number of tickets to the 2pm and 7pm shows in the same transaction and receive a discount at checkout!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/upcoming-events/big-shiny-tunes-kelowna-7pm-show\">Click here for the 7pm Big Shiny Tunes Kelowna!</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Big Shiny Tunes Kelowna</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
