<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/338601ASCBNPJRTGSPTCNCCLHLKSLTRJD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Brent Butt in Kelowna";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b38ebc23-039f-4cde-acb6-429cf0fb5ece.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Gateway Events presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">BRENT BUTT IN KELOWNA</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience advisory: Mature content</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Brent Butt has long been considered one of the funniest people in Canada, with a career in stand-up comedy that stretches into five decades, including numerous appearances at major festivals in multiple countries and being voted Best Male Stand-Up in Canada by his peers in the profession. He also created and starred in two successful sitcoms – CORNER GAS (“Funniest Show on TV” as voted by TV Guide Readers, currently in 60 countries) and HICCUPS (multiple Leo and Writers Guild Awards).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">About Damonde Tschritter</span> <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/slimtschridy/\">https://www.instagram.com/slimtschridy/</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This Canadian Comedy Award Nominee has had his own one hour national TV special on CTV and Comedy Network as well as CBC appearances on The Debaters, Just For Laughs, Winnipeg Comedy Festival, LOL, Madly Off in All Directions, and many more. He has over forty film and television credits with his most recent being HBO’s The Making of A Comedy Special with Conan O’Brien. His first feature film The Opener which he wrote and directed is slated for release in 2026.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $64.46</span>  ($54.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Brent Butt in Kelowna</span> tickets and fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
