	</table><span><br/></span>An Evening with the Anna Jacyszyn Quintet.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Step into a winter wonderland of melody as award-winning vocalist Anna Jacyszyn brings to life \"Christmas Presence!\" her annual signature holiday concert. This beloved tradition, which has warmed hearts since 2015, blends original seasonal compositions with jazz-infused Christmas classics. This year they have added a matinee at 2 p.m. as well as the evening 7:30 p.m. and both promise to sparkle like freshly fallen snow. Join in the festive spirit with audience sing-alongs of seasonal favorites and a candlelit hymn guaranteed to carry the joy of the season all the way home. Don't miss this enchanting holiday tradition that sells out year after year – where every note feels like a gift and every song celebrates the true presence of Christmas magic.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Experience the magic of Anna's original holiday hits including \"Snow Day,\" \"Cashmere and Love,\" “Tis the Season for Love”, “Clink Cheer” and the sentimental heartfelt “Holly Day” - all wrapped in the warm embrace of jazz, blues, and soul. Backed by an all-star ensemble featuring Stu Goldberg (piano), Scott Gamble (drums), Stefan Bienz (double bass), and Stephen Buck (woodwinds).<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $42.61</span>  ($35.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.25 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child under 12  $36.86</span>  ($30.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Christmas Presence!</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
