<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/364801AJMNRNBCJRNTQQHKJTJHQMDNPPH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CMK - Notos Piano Quartet";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/0f483250-9e1b-4b58-8325-1964e9a3f5ca.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Chamber Music Kelowna presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">NOTOS PIANO QUARTET</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Since their formation in 2007, the four musicians have earned six first prizes along with numerous special awards at international competitions in the Netherlands, Italy, England, and China, establishing a strong presence on the global stage. The Quartet has performed in renowned concert halls across Europe and has also toured internationally in Australia, the United States, China, Japan, South Africa, and Southeast Asia. In 2022, the Notos Quartet received the prestigious Würth Prize from Jeunesses Musicales. Alongside performing well-known masterpieces, the quartet regularly commissions and premieres new works for piano quartet. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $67.50</span>  ($56.34 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.80 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student (w/ID)  $25.00</span>  ($19.38 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.26 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Notos Piano Quartet</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
