<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/315801ASRPRBJCLVNNQLLQQMDKMDHLNSC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Colin James Blues Trio";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/7c45e0e2-c178-4c72-92af-caff7f37d5f6.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kootenay Concert Connection presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">COLIN JAMES BLUES TRIO</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This show is SOLD OUT! <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/waitlist\">Click here to join the waitlist</a></span>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From the prairies of Saskatchewan to the stages of the world, Colin James has shared his talent with some of the greatest and most influential musicians of all time. With 21 studio albums behind him, a six-time Juno award winning singer/songwriter, and multiple Maple Blues Award winner, Colin James has steadily established himself as one of Canada’s greatest musicians. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With a career spanning over three decades, Colin continues to sell out from coast to coast with his electrifying stage performances and superb guitar prowess. Joining Colin on this latest tour are two notable and accomplished sidemen, Kenny Neal and Chris Caddell, making for a great evening of entertainment. The Colin James Blue Trio live in May of next year is a presentation of the Kootenay Concert Connection. You are advised to get your tickets early to avoid disappointment as his last tour of the interior in 2024 SOLD OUT at every single venue it played. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $69.06</span>  ($58.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.70 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Colin James Blues Trio</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-20T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/7c45e0e2-c178-4c72-92af-caff7f37d5f6.jpg>;
