<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/382401ABHCJSPTPLKVPRDLNRNNCSNRQTG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Eddy's Kingdom";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Artaban Productions presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">EDDY'S KINGDOM</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>In this stranger-than-fiction documentary, Eddy Haymour's obsessive dream of developing Rattlesnake Island in to Middle Eastern-themed amusement park leads to a spiralling path of legal turmoil and financial ruin, with a hostage-taking and bomb plots along the way. This is Okanagan history like you've never heard it! The director will be at the screening for a Q and A.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular $20.00</span>  ($15.01 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Eddy's Kingdom</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
