<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/364202ADQQQDTBPMVHTHCQQCDDCCRGDKR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "FireSmart Registration";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Protecting your community from wildfire threats begins with you!</h1><span><br/></span>Thanks for helping make our community FireSmart, Kelowna!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The Kelowna FireSmart Community Chipping program returns this spring, with pickups scheduled to begin May 4, 2026</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This page is for registration only for the FireSmart Community Chipping Program. <span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Please Note:</span> you do not need to print any tickets for this registration - but please continue with \"buy tickets\" - once you confirm your spot you will receive an email from the Kelowna Fire Department with information around your date of pick-up. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Participants who are accepted into the program will receive an email confirming their spot, preparation requirements, and acceptable materials. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The FireSmart Community Chipping Program offers free curbside removal and chipping of select highly flammable plants and shrubs to help reduce wildfire risk on residential properties in Kelowna. Space in the program is limited, and registrations will be capped once all available pickup slots are filled. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Only select materials are considered highly flammable and eligible for pickup through this program. You will be asked to \"Is your pile only approved flammable materials?\" Please confirm that your pile consists only of cedar, juniper, mugo pine, conifer branches and prunings. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Thank you to everyone for your interest in helping reduce wildfire risk in our community! </h2>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-04T08:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/d8d55cc7-24ec-446a-ae79-cf246c5e2ad7.jpg>;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/location/9001AGHDBMPJDRPSRMKLRCJGBJJMTQGDH>;
  schema:duration "PT60M";
  schema:endDate "2026-05-04T09:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime .

<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/360801AJTKRDCBJLBLRLHMPGJTGHNTVVH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Flip Flop Gala";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/b67d9330-279b-411b-947e-7e218279df7a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Touchdown Kelowna presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">FLIP FLOP GALA</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Where Black Tie Meets Barefoot</span></span></h2>An exclusive, one‑night‑only celebration on Kelowna’s waterfront — deliberately breaking the rules of what a gala can be.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">The Flip Flop Gala</span> is an elevated Okanagan experience designed for those who appreciate contrast: formal elegance paired with laid‑back confidence, refinement with a wink, prestige without pretence.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Set directly in front of the Waterfront Performance Stage, guests are placed at the very centre of the experience - not watching from the sidelines, but part of the moment itself.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">This is not a typical gala.</span></h2>Expect tuxedos and bow ties. Sequins and silk.<span><br/></span>And beneath the elegance? Flip flops. Bare feet. Sandals.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Formal on top. Beach on the bottom.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s elevated irreverence.<span><br/></span>Sophisticated yet unbuttoned.<span><br/></span>High‑energy yet intentionally intimate.<span><br/></span>Proudly local. Unexpected. Unmistakably Kelowna.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As the night unfolds, curated lighting and sound transform the waterfront into a cinematic open‑air venue. A live DJ set sets the tone, while surprise, organic moments — familiar local faces, subtle hometown nods - emerge naturally throughout the evening.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>There are no velvet ropes here.<span><br/></span>No backstage. No VIP separation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Guests mingle freely, from the dance floor to bespoke cabana‑style lounge spaces designed for conversation, connection, and people‑watching.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">An intentionally limited experience.</span><span><br/></span>Your ticket includes:<span><br/></span><ul><li>A welcome cocktail on arrival</li><li>Elevated food grazing stations showcasing local flavours</li></ul>Additional beverages will be available for purchase throughout the evening.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are intentionally limited to preserve the intimacy and atmosphere of the event.<span><br/></span>Once tickets are sold out - that’s it.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Additional information</span><span><br/></span><ul><li><span class=\"BoldText\">19+ event</span></li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Gates open at 7:00 pm</span></li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Themed attire encouraged</span> (confidence required - there’s no wrong interpretation)</li><li><span class=\"BoldText\">Rain or shine</span> - the waterfront sets the mood either way</li></ul>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">General  $181.13</span>  ($157.75 base price + $23.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Flip Flop Gala</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-06-29T19:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
