<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/318801ASMQTKVVPRHHQRHPBSKTGMNJQMD>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Gaslight";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/5c5453d6-628b-4db9-af5a-3691418c1c6c.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>New Vintage Theatre presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">GASLIGHT</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">Based on the play by Patrick Hamilton</span></h2><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">by Johnna Wright & Patty Jamieson</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"I know it sounds mad, but I think there is something-someone, up in the attic\"<span><br/></span>Bella Manningham thinks she is losing her mind. Every night there are strange sounds and the gas lights dim for no reason. Is she losing her sense of reality or is it being loosened for her? Don't miss this thriller, reimagined for the stage in this hit Canadian adaptation first seen at the Shaw Festival. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $48.71</span>  ($40.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student/Senior  $42.96</span>  ($35.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.60 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Gaslight</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
