<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/383601ALNVDGGDLHNDQBBPMRBHMJQCHLC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Gilea Dance Celebration";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Gilea Dance Academy presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">GILEA DANCE CELEBRATION</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join us for Gilea Dance Academy’s Season Finale Dance Presentation — an inspiring showcase where our dancers share everything they’ve learned, created, and accomplished this year. This special event brings together parents, friends, and our wider community to celebrate the artistry, dedication, and joy that fill our studios every day.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From our youngest beginners to our advanced performers, each class will take the stage with choreography that highlights their progress, confidence, and unique expression. Expect a vibrant mix of styles, heartfelt moments, and the unmistakable spirit of Gilea: inclusivity, creativity, and the belief that dance is for everyone.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>We can’t wait to share this memorable evening with you and cheer on our dancers as they shine.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $26.51</span>  ($21.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.15 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior (65+) $24.10</span>   ($18.90 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.84 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student (12-18) $17.59</span>  ($12.60 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child  (5-11) $10.24</span>  ($5.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Children 5 and under are free, pre-registration is required.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Gilea Dance Celebration</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
