<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/371801AJPMVMPMGHCRPLSHLSCNVJPMKDM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "In My Mind; Stillness in the Storm";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/fd9a9755-4fde-4b85-b302-59ade19dfaa5.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Creator's Arts Centre presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">IN MY MIND; STILLNESS IN THE STORM</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>What happens inside our minds when the world feels loud, busy, or overwhelming? Through movement, music, and expression, our dancers bring these moments to life in a way that is both powerful and uplifting.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From our youngest dancers to our senior performers, each piece captures a different emotion, wonder, calm, uncertainty, and strength. Woven together into a beautiful journey of self-expression.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At its heart, this show is about finding light, even on cloudy days. We invite you to sit back, feel, and be inspired by the stories our dancers are ready to share.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student/Child  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">In My Mind; Stillness in The Storm</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
