<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/367601APQMBHLSCCMMDQLLCKTRKKJVVGG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "KCCA - Schmaltz & Pepper";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/3ae464e9-ab64-4f44-bfd7-93d77f4283b0.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Community Concert Association presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SCHMALTZ & PEPPER</span></h1><h2>KCCA 2026-2027 Series</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>It’s a mouthwatering recipe: Mix together five powerhouse Canadian musicians. Add multi-instrumental virtuosity. Fold in generous dollops of creativity, energy, and unbridled joy. Garnish with JUNO and Grammy tributes. The result is Schmaltz & Pepper, a sizzling and satisfying new chamber ensemble that blends Klezmer, modern jazz, Roma, Tango, classical and European folk music into pure musical magic. <span class=\"ItalicText\">Bon appétit!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Website: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.schmaltzandpepper.com/\">schmaltzandpepper.com</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This concert is part of the Kelowna Community Concert Association’s 2026/2027 season, composed of five world-class concerts. The subscription price is uniquely affordable and the best way to secure a ticket to this show.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/kelowna-community-concert-association\">Find full details on the season and the subscription here.</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Single tickets for this concert will be available in very limited quantities a minimum of two weeks prior to the concert. Prices for individual tickets will vary.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Schmaltz & Pepper</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
