<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/367801ADVMBBKCRVMPDTMJVCVJVSCGCCT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "KCCA - The Fugitives";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/e092d892-2fec-4a0e-9284-6ce8b915e59a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Community Concert Association presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE FUGITIVES</span></h1><h2>KCCA 2026-2027 Series</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Just before Remembrance Day we bring back The Fugitives, an extraordinarily talented Canadian folk ensemble, to perform Ridge, their moving tribute to the 10,000 young men and boys whose lives were lost or forever changed at the Battle of Vimy Ridge. Deeply-researched and widely-acclaimed, Ridge blends complex harmonies and top-tier musicianship with storytelling based on firsthand accounts, including the young soldiers’ poignant letters home. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Website: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.fugitives.ca\">fugitives.ca</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">This concert is part of the Kelowna Community Concert Association’s 2026/2027 season, composed of five world-class concerts. The subscription price is uniquely affordable and the best way to secure a ticket to this show.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/kelowna-community-concert-association\">Find full details on the season and the subscription here.</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Single tickets for this concert will be available in very limited quantities a minimum of two weeks prior to the concert. Prices for individual tickets will vary.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Fugitives</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
