  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Kelowna Dance - A Celebration of Dance";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Dance and Performing Arts presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">A CELEBRATION OF DANCE</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join us for the 16th Annual Celebration of Dance - an inspiring showcase of talent, passion, and creativity featuring Dancers of all ages and styles. Enjoy an unforgettable performance at our 1pm matinee or 6pm evening show as we celebrate another year of Dance!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $39.16</span>  ($32.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.80 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student  $36.86</span>  ($30.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $36.86</span>  ($30.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">A Celebration of Dance</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
