<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/381001AQSTMGMBVPRMDPMNBDHRKGJLJNG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Meet the City - Municipal Money Matters";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/0f88a564-57bc-4681-8689-9ec72077913a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>WSP Canada presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MEET THE CITY - MUNICIPAL MONEY MATTERS</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">In collaboration with the City of Kelowna</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The 4th Annual Meet the City Event is here. MUNICIPAL MONEY MATTERS. This year the event will take on a new focus, with discussion centered around trust, transparency and accountability in local government.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>The challenges of the past few years are well known: rapid inflation adding major financial pressures to governments, businesses and families alike; escalating mental health and addictions struggles; significant demographic and migration shifts, compounded by a housing crisis; and political polarization.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>Some current data trends suggest the relationship between local government and the communities they serve is changing: from declines in voter turnout and number of candidates seeking elected office at the local level, to broader declines in public trust in government in democracies around the world.<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>Speakers from the City's Finance, Development and Real Estate teams will provide a transparent and accountable look into spending and issues that matter to you. See you there.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Admission is a suggested $10.00 donation. All proceeds go to the Kelowna Food Bank.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">In order to ensure availability of tickets, we kindly request that attendance is limited to 2 per company.</span>
""";
