<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/369001ASBDJJMQLDCTNJQLPLBTTLTCKBL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Music Fest MS";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/15600e7e-315f-4504-85fb-e22590f9d8a4.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Klick Entertainment presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MUSIC FEST MS</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>\"Music Fest MS\" is a charity fundraiser in support of Multiple Sclerosis. Tickets and donations are given to MS Canada to support research initiatives to find a cure for MS. To date, this show has raised over $170,000. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This unique event features a \"Nashville Songwriters Round\" where professional artists and songwriters share the stories behind their songs. You'll hear #1 hits played on the radio, songs that have been put on hold by major artists, and songs from local performers around the Okanagan valley. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Fight. Play. Feel. Live. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Be a part of the growing community and support group, and let's put an end to Multiple Sclerosis.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $25.00</span>  ($19.38 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.26 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Music Fest MS</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
