<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/353201ALBLRLVMRCLTRDDLLKDKBHBNJPS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Okanagan Fight Night 8";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/5ba60dd8-c93a-40c8-af76-6cb0dd213182.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Victory International Promotion presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">OKANAGAN FIGHT NIGHT 8</span> </h1><h2>Bigger moments. Higher stakes. Same electric energy.</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The Okanagan’s premier combat sports event returns—and Fight Night 8 is already shaping up to be another unforgettable night. With the roar of the crowd, the intensity of live competition, and the unmistakable atmosphere, this is the event fans mark on their calendars months in advance.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>While the fight card is still under wraps, one thing is guaranteed: a high-energy night packed with elite talent, hard-hitting action, and the kind of live experience you can only get inside the venue. From the first walkout to the final bell, Fight Night 8 delivers nonstop excitement and an atmosphere that keeps Kelowna buzzing long after the lights go down.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Seats always move fast. Secure yours early and lock in your spot before the lineup is announced. Bring the crew. Feel the energy. Be there when Fight Night returns.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This isn’t just another event—it’s <span class=\"BoldText\">Okanagan Fight Night 8</span>.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Reserve your tickets now and be part of the next chapter.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $77.11</span>  ($65.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Okanagan Fight Night 7</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-05-23T18:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/5ba60dd8-c93a-40c8-af76-6cb0dd213182.jpg>;
