<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/376801ARKTGMRHLRVJSBCSLCMSVQQBDMV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO 1 - Music That Shimmers (Kelowna)";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/11e82d8b-631f-4764-b447-20196f78f11f.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MUSIC THAT SHIMMERS</span></h1><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">CONDUCTOR: Jullian Pellicano</span></h2><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\"> featuring Joy Yeh, harp.</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Celebrate opening night with the Okanagan Symphony Orchestra, music director Julian Pellicano and a program designed to lift your spirits! Featuring Goulet’s delectable Symphonic Chocolates, internationally celebrated harpist Joy Yeh in Glière’s sparkling harp concerto, and closing in grand style with Handel’s Music for the Royal Fireworks, this is a shining start to the season, music that truly shimmers. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This concert features Maxime Goulet's \"Chocolats symphonique,\" pairing a different chocolate with each movement for a multi-sensory experience. Renew or purchase a Season Pass before June 30 and your chocolate tasting is included! As of July 2, purchasing the chocolate tasting will add $12 per person to your Season Pass or single ticket.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>--
<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Section A</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $75.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $11.25 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$88.61</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $56.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.44 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$67.05</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section B</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $63.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.56 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$75.67</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $45.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.75 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$54.11</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$23.06</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section C</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $37.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$45.49</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $37.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$45.49</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$23.06</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - age 65yrs+, Youth - up to age 24yrs.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Okanagan Symphony Orchestra <span class=\"BoldText\">Music That Shimmers</span> tickets and applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
