  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO 3 - Freya & Friends (Kelowna)";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/4c39e2fb-6aab-48f2-b484-824f50a43703.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">FREYA & FRIENDS</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">featuring Freya, Jazz vocalist Leila Naderi, and the Okanagan Symphony Chorus</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>An undisputed hit in 2025, folk duo Freya returns with music that will touch your heart and soul. <span class=\"BoldText\">Freya & Friends</span> expands their signature warmth, welcoming Okanagan-based jazz vocalist Leila Naderi, weaving new songs and reimagining favorites. The Okanagan Symphony Chorus joins the Orchestra for a holiday concert that renews the magic while charting new ground for the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>--
