<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/379201ATHSQQQHJTVQMQMKNHPTPCHVTVQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OSO 7 - Season Finale (Penticton)";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/ba73cb50-fbb9-4c44-b10d-9820e407141a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Okanagan Symphony Orchestra presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SEASON FINALE</span></h1><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">CONDUCTOR: Julian Pellicano</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>In a special partnership with the National Arts Centre Orchestra, the Okanagan Symphony Orchestra proudly presents the BC premiere of Jean Coulthard’s long overlooked Symphony No. 1, reviving a major work by one of Canada’s most influential 20th century composers. Paired with Brahms’ Symphony No. 1, music director Julian Pellicano conducts a concert that unites a rediscovered Canadian symphony with one of the great pillars of the orchestral repertoire.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>--
<span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Section A</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $75.00 base price + $11.25 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$86.25</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $56.25 base price + $8.44 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$64.69</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section B</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $63.75 base price + $9.56 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$73.31</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $45.00 base price + $6.75 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$51.75</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$20.70</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Section C</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult</span> $37.50 base price + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$43.13</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior</span> $37.50 base price + $5.63 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$43.13</span> total price<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth</span> $18.00 base price + $2.70 service charge = <span class=\"BoldText\">$20.70</span> total price<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Senior - age 65yrs+, Youth - up to age 24yrs.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. Okanagan Symphony Orchestra <span class=\"BoldText\">Season Finale</span> tickets and applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
