<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/370201ANCGBSPVMRCTGHDQSPMTPSMPPDL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "OVATION Gala";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/2d882d29-ba88-4d0d-8484-dbc0b5d02b0a.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Central Okanagan Performing Arts Festival presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">OVATION GALA</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join us for OVATION, an unforgettable evening celebrating the incredible talent and dedication of COPAF performers.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The evening begins from 5:30 – 6:30 PM with a warm and welcoming reception, where guests can enjoy food, drinks, and the opportunity to connect with fellow artists, families, and community members in a relaxed and celebratory atmosphere.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At 6:30 PM, the spotlight turns to the stage for a dynamic showcase of local excellence. From 6:30 – 7:20 PM, audiences will experience a curated selection of standout performances in dance, piano, strings, and voice, highlighting the artistry and hard work of this year’s festival participants.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Following a short intermission, the evening continues from 7:35 – 8:30 PM with a very special guest performance by CANDESCA, bringing a powerful and memorable close to the night. The evening will also feature the presentation of awards and scholarships, recognizing outstanding achievement and dedication across the festival.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>OVATION is a celebration of community, creativity, and the next generation of performing artists. We look forward to sharing this inspiring evening with you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult (18+) $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Youth (Ages 13-17)  $14.99</span>  ($10.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Child (12 and under) free admission, pre-registration required</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">OVATION Gala</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
