<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/362801APKSVDTPQGQVHGMHBJSBTTGVDPC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Queen - It's a Kinda Magic";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/78331f1e-ddbd-4756-a96b-8b84fcd763eb.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Johnny Showtime Ltd. presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">QUEEN</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">It's a Kinda Magic</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>ARE YOU READY TO ROCK?! Direct from Australia, the hit tribute returns to Canada in 2026 - bigger, better and louder than ever!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See the rock spectacular that Canadians flock to every year, bringing big sound, big screens, crazy lighting and outlandish costumes for a night of non-stop rock anthems, including Bohemian Rhapsody, We Will Rock You, We Are the Champions, Radio GaGa, I Want to Break Free, Somebody to Love, Don’t Stop Me Now, Another One Bites the Dust and so many more.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Starring Warren Vernon-Driscoll reprising his role as ‘Freddie Mercury’, performing vocals, piano and guitar all live on stage and in original key, alongside an international band.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss the REAL ROCK EXPERIENCE – BOOK NOW!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“Live, loud and literally awe-smacked”</span> - Stage & Screen<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“It felt like a real Queen concert”</span> - Vancouvers Best Places<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">“This is THE tribute band”</span> - The Plus Ones<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iVhtVTsCuJs\">Check out the promo trailer here!</a></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Website</span>: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://showtime.net.au/shows/queen-its-a-kinda-magic/\">queenitsakindamagic.com</a><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Facebook </span>: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/queenitsakindamagic\">queenitsakindamagic</a><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Instagram</span> : <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/queenIAKMshow/\">queeniakmshow</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $79.00</span>  ($66.64 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child (13 and under)  $49.00</span>  ($40.56 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.08 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Grab your tickets now—Early Bird pricing is on until April 30!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Queen: It's a Kinda Magic</span> tickets and fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
