<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/376601ADPRDDGRRPGQDDRHGGBKRVLVVHL>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "RCA Presents 2026/27 Season Launch";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/3efd1965-e8fb-4ead-9bda-d715d8416e79.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Rotary Centre for the Arts presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">RCA PRESENTS 2026/27 SEASON LAUNCH</span> </h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">ft. Mickey Reeves, and White Sails A Capella Chorus</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join us for an exciting evening as we launch the 2026–2027 RCA Presents season. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Be among the first to experience what’s coming next with an exclusive preview presented by Theatre Programming Director Andrew Stauffer, as well as performances by: <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Mickey Reeves</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>An innovative banjo player blending bluegrass, jazz, and classical influences into a truly distinctive sound. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Singers from White Sails A Cappella Chorus</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A dynamic and engaging sextet delivering rich harmonies and the joyful energy of women’s barbershop. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>As our guest, you’ll get early insight into the full season lineup and a first look at the shows coming to the Mary Irwin Theatre. <span><br/></span>
""";
