<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/362401ALBRHRDDHTQMPHNDCGQRCJVKHML>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Rhythm of Punjab";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Simranjeet Kaur presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">RHYTHM OF PUNJAB</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Rhythm of Punjab, organized by Moon Star Entertainment Ltd, is a high-energy cultural concert celebrating the vibrant spirit of Punjabi music and tradition. Experience an unforgettable night featuring multiple celebrated singers, live performances, and dynamic bhangra dance acts. This showcase brings together the rich heritage, rhythm, and colourful culture of Punjab on one stage. Join us for an evening filled with music, dance, and pure Punjabi festivity!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP  $250.00</span>  ($215.34 base price + $2.36 CIF + $32.30 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $185.00</span>  ($158.82 base price + $2.36 CIF + $23.82 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior - 65+ - $145.00</span>  ($124.03 base price + $2.36 CIF + $18.61 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $145.00</span>  ($124.03 base price + $2.36 CIF + $18.61 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Rhythm of Punjab</span> tickets and fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
