  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Sing Out Kelowna 2026";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/05b41fd2-32ea-4493-8abd-3965fd54d012.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Secondary School presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SING OUT KELOWNA 2026</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Sing Out Kelowna is a musical event showcasing choral music in the Central Okanagan public school system. Choirs from Kelowna Secondary School, Rutland Secondary, Mt. Boucherie Secondary, OKM Secondary, and Dr. Knox Secondary will be performing at Kelowna Community Theatre.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $20.00</span> ($15.01 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Sing Out Kelowna 2026</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
