  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Singin' in the Rain Jr";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/61056c1e-4ec9-4440-8b3c-efd3f3f66080.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Kelowna Arts Academy presents</h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">SINGIN' IN THE RAIN JR.</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Fun for the whole family!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This show is a perfect for young theatre goers, with it's hilarious situations, snappy dialogue and a hit-parade score of Hollywood standards. In silent movies, Don Lockwood and Lina Lamont are a hot item, but behind the scenes, things aren't always as they appear on the big screen! Meanwhile, Lina's squeaky voice might be the end of her career in \"talking pictures\" without the help of a talented young actress to do the talking and singing for her.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Early Bird (evening shows through April 30th)</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $19.99</span>  ($15.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Regular Pricing (May 1st onward)</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Evening show  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Matinee show  $10.00</span>  ($5.01 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Singin' in the Rain Jr.</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
