<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/317802AKNSLRLGMGJRSTKCNHVGBRJDKSJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Stage Fright: Musical Theatre Cabaret";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/edda1bbd-ef5e-4064-856f-3a30637cdf9c.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>New Vintage Theatre presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">STAGE FRIGHT</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">Spooky Season Musical Theatre Cabaret</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>New Vintage Theatre artists perform our favourite Hallowe'en hits and chilling new scenes at these fundraiser evenings that are spectacularly thrilling. Each guest receives a mystery box and fortune telling with their entry. Grab your costume and get your tickets early for this highly anti-ci-pated event. All funds raised go to our theatre school and to the planning of our 15th anniversary season. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>General seating - first rows reserved for Season Ticket Holders.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $44.00</span>  ($40.00 base price + $4.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student/Senior  $38.50</span>  ($35.00 base price + $3.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Stage Fright</span> tickets and service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
