<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/375201ARVBVGHJVCMTKNKLTCVCPSMKRGN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Stardust: A Diamond Heist Dance Cabaret";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/1fb195fa-bef2-4970-9c33-366ae8d7823e.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>The Lolas present </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">STARDUST</span> </h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">A Diamond Heist Dance Cabaret</span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Stardust is a dazzling, wordless spy-themed dance comedy where cabaret meets cartoon chaos. Three rival teams of showgirl spies battle through mistaken identities, heists, and heartbreak in pursuit of the stolen Stardust Diamond. Set to a high-energy soundtrack and packed with slapstick humour, cinematic choreography, and a hint of romance, Stardust delivers spectacle, sass, and nonstop physical storytelling that transcends language. Think Austin Powers meets Moulin Rouge — glamorous, funny, and full of surprises.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The show is suitable for most audiences, though due to slapstick style comedy and some scenes with implied alcohol consumption, discretion is advised for viewers under the age of 13. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Trailer link: <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shorts/fIHcZ36WRqo\">https://www.youtube.com/shorts/fIHcZ36WRqo</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Zone A</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult $86.03</span>  ($72.45 base price + $2.36 CIF  + $11.22 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $73.53</span>  ($61.58 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.59 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student  $73.53</span>  ($61.58 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.59 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child  $73.53</span>  ($61.58 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.59 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Zone B</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $73.96</span>  ($61.95 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.65 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $63.27</span>  ($52.66 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.25 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student  $63.27</span>  ($52.66 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.25 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child  $63.27</span>  ($52.66 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.25 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Zone C</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult $61.42</span>  ($51.05 base price + $2.36 CIF + $8.01 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior  $52.61</span>  ($43.39 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.86 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student  $52.61</span>  ($43.39 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.86 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child  $52.61</span>  ($43.39 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.86 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span>Student (ID required) • Kids under 12 • Seniors 65+<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Stardust: A Diamond Heist Dance Cabaret</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
