<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/380601APHJTNBSHLLSPCHVPCGMDVSGNHS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Tarsem Jassar";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/24e2fab2-5204-4316-93fa-63a7c8e69947.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Pita Pit presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">TARSEM JASSAR</span></h1><h2>World Is Yours Tour 2026 | Canada</h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>After an incredible four-year absence, <span class=\"BoldText\">Tarsem Jassar</span> returns to Canada - bigger, bolder, and more powerful than ever.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Happy Slice and Pita Pit proudly presents the Kelowna leg of <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">World Is Yours Tour 2026 - Canada</span></span>, a landmark live experience that goes far beyond a traditional concert. This is a full-scale production where music, culture, and cinematic legacy collide on one unforgettable stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Globally celebrated for his commanding presence, poetic lyricism, and deep roots in Punjabi culture, Tarsem Jassar has become one of the most influential voices in contemporary Punjabi music and cinema. The World Is Yours Tour represents a defining moment in his career - delivering chart-topping hits, powerful storytelling, and immersive visuals in a show designed to inspire and electrify fans.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Audiences can expect:</span><span><br/></span><ul><li>A high-energy live performance featuring Tarsem Jassar’s most iconic songs</li><li>Cinematic staging and visuals that elevate the concert into a cultural experience</li><li>A night that celebrates Punjabi pride, artistry, and global influence</li></ul><span><br/></span>Whether you’ve followed Tarsem Jassar from the beginning or are discovering his music live for the first time, this tour promises an unmatched atmosphere and unforgettable energy.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">One artist. One vision. One world-class experience.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets are limited. Secure your seats early for this must-see live event.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP 1  $289.86</span>  ($250.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $37.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">VIP 2  $232.36</span>  ($200.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $30.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 1  $174.86</span>  ($150.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $22.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 2  $146.11</span>  ($125.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $18.75 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 3  $94.36</span>  ($80.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $12.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 4  $71.36</span>  ($60.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $9.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Tier 5  $59.86</span>  ($50.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.50 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Tarsem Jassar</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
