<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/372801APGBSLRDTVPQJMLGDRTQMPKCRBH>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Dream Dance Club Experience: 2026";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/8a797d2b-fc18-4c5b-a98e-34e3ce434fe0.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Dream Dance Club presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE DREAM DANCE CLUB EXPERIENCE 2026</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Join us for a truly special evening as we celebrate 10 seasons of Dream Dance Club.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This night is a celebration of everything that has gone into building our studio — the years of dedication, love for dance, and the passion shared by our dancers, families, and teachers. Dream Dance Club is more than a studio, it’s a family, and this recital reflects that.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>From our beginner teams to our most accomplished dancers, each performance represents not just this season, but the growth, commitment, and journey each dancer has been on.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>It’s a night full of talent, heart, and something truly special. We can’t wait to celebrate with you.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $32.90</span>  ($26.25 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.29 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child under 5  $20.74</span>  ($15.75 base price + $2.36 CIF + $2.63 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Dream Dance Club Experience 2026</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
