<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/371601ACNPCSQVDGJDQNLJNVKBNMDSVPM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Journey We Make";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/161b6e45-e512-4e0f-9316-1f9b1fd71a38.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Creator's Arts Centre presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE JOURNEY WE MAKE</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>The Journey We Make celebrates the growth, strength, and passion our dancers have developed along the way. This year’s competitive showcase brings together inspiring music and powerful choreography.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>At its core, this is a showcase of the Impact Competitive Program — a training environment where dancers grow not only as performers, but as people. Through competition, Impact dancers learn essential life skills including resilience, discipline, teamwork, commitment, time management, confidence under pressure, goal setting, and sportsmanship. These lessons extend far beyond the stage and into everyday life.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The evening also shares the heart behind the program. Proceeds from the showcase support Creator’s Arts Centre’s Tuition Assistance Program, and initiatives that help ensure financial barriers never prevent a dancer from accessing high‑quality arts education.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re cheering on a performer, discovering Impact for the first time, or simply enjoying an energetic night of performance, join us as we honour the artistry, growth, and community that creates The Journey We Make.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $31.46</span>  ($25.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.10 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student/Child  $25.71</span>  ($20.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $3.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Mary Irwin Theatre at the Rotary Centre for the Arts event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Journey We Make</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
