<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/306001ANGKVKQJMSPKGHBHCBLDGBBTLVQ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Michael Jackson HIStory Show";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/e48fea12-8dcd-404d-b6d9-e3abbf8aa358.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Johnny Showtime presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THE MICHAEL JACKSON HISTORY SHOW</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Don’t miss your chance to see Showtime’s <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The Michael Jackson HIStory Show</span></span> – returning to Canada in 2026 to commemorate 30 years since Michael Jackson’s final, ground-breaking world tour: HISTORY.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Celebrate Jackson’s creative genius and unsurpassed talent with riveting live performances covering his early days as a member of the Jackson 5, his groundbreaking theatrics in the 80s and his continued domination of Pop culture into the 21st century.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>See the famous music videos come to life, and hear all the hits performed live, including \"Thriller\", \"Billie Jean\", \"Smooth Criminal\", \"Bad, \"Beat It\", \"ABC\", \"Don’t Stop Til You Get Enough\", \"Human Nature\", \"PYT\", \"They Don’t Really Care About Us\" and many more.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Garth Field is electrifying in his role as Jackson, accompanied by a live band, choreographed dancers, authentic costumes, state-of-the-art sound and theatrical lighting, vision and effects. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Truly a mind-blowing stage production – book now to secure your seats close to the action!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">*This is a tribute show and is not associated with the Estate of Michael Jackson.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Audience Advisory: use of strobe, haze and smoke.</span></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $81.71</span>  ($69.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $10.35 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Child (under 13)  $48.36</span>  ($40.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $6.00 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Group Rate available for groups of 6 or more when purchased in a single transaction!</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">Michael Jackson HIStory</span> tickets and their applicable fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
