	</table><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Feel the Adrenaline…Feel the VIBE!</span></span></h2>April 23–26, 2026 | Kelowna Community Theatre<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for The Vibe Dance Competition, where dancers from across British Columbia and Alberta come together to showcase their talent and passion. Experience a variety of dance genres and support these dedicated performers in an event that promises excitement and inspiration.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Event Schedule:</span></span><span><br/></span>Thursday, April 23: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM<span><br/></span>Friday, April 24: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM<span><br/></span>Saturday, April 25: 9:00 AM – 10:00 PM<span><br/></span>Sunday, April 26: 9:00 AM – 6:45 PM<span><br/></span>Sunday, Battle of The Vibe: 7:45 PM – 9:00 PM<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ticket Options:</span></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">1-Day Pass:</span> Access to any single day – $10.00 <span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">2-Day Pass:</span> Access on Saturday and Sunday, including Battle of The Vibe – $15.00<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">3-Day Pass:</span> Access from Friday to Sunday, including Battle of The Vibe – $20.00 <span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">4-Day Pass:</span> Full access from Thursday to Sunday, including Battle of The Vibe – $25.00<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Note: Battle of The Vibe admission is only included in Multi-Day Passes.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.theboxoffice.ca/upcoming-events/battle-vibe\">Click here for Battle of The Vibe tickets</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><spa