<http://www.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/event/328201ARCPPSQCNPNRGVCPKPSQHMMNPPR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "This Is Adele: A Tribute to Adele";
  schema:description """
	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/e76a4914-70b2-4d6f-8bb5-b5125dd109ee.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>Wax Pencil Imagery presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">THIS IS ADELE</span></h1><h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">A Tribute to Adele</span></span></h2></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>Experience the power and emotion of Adele's greatest hits in this unforgettable tribute performance featuring singer, songwriter and multi-instrumentalist Amanda Bentley as Adele. Amanda brings her years of experience and refined vocal skillset to the stage and combines it with heartfelt story telling and the timeless glamour Adele is known for. This show captures the spirit, charm and raw honesty of her music. From soaring ballads to powerful anthems, you'll be taken on a journey through the songs that have touched millions around the world. Backed by a world class six piece band, this show is perfect for all ages and offers an authentic, moving and entertaining night you won't soon forget.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Regular  $62.74</span>  ($52.50 base price + $2.36 CIF + $7.88 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.25 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF) and 5% GST. A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">This Is Adele</span> service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
