  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Touchdown Kelowna - Corporate Packages";
  schema:description """
	<img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/3c71672c-f0e9-4e32-94a6-a4d9c05806ea.jpg\" /> <span><br/></span><h2>An Unforgettable Week of Football, Music & Celebration</h2><span><br/></span>Touchdown Kelowna is shaping up to be one of the most exciting event weeks Kelowna has ever hosted - and this exclusive corporate package offers one of the only remaining ways to be part of it in a truly meaningful way.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Designed for client appreciation, team recognition, or partner hosting, the Touchdown Kelowna Corporate Package brings together sold‑out professional football, headline live music, and one of the festival’s most talked‑about social events - all in one seamless, turnkey booking.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>With limited quantities available, this is a rare opportunity to secure premium access to experiences that can no longer be purchased individually.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">What’s Included</span></h2><span class=\"ItalicText\">50 tickets across five headline Touchdown Kelowna events</span><span><br/></span>🏈 <span class=\"BoldText\">BC Lions Games - End Zone Grandstand</span><span><br/></span>Enjoy premium end‑zone grandstand seating at both sold-out BC Lions home games in Kelowna.<span><br/></span>10 tickets - Saturday, 27 June: BC Lions vs Calgary Stampeders<span><br/></span>10 tickets -Saturday, 4 July: BC Lions vs Edmonton Elks<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>🎶 <span class=\"BoldText\">Headline Concerts - Waterfront Park</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Take in two of Touchdown Kelowna’s signature outdoor concerts at the waterfront.</span><span><br/></span>10 tickets - Friday, 26 June: Alan Doyle<span><br/></span>10 tickets - Friday, 3 July: The Road Hammers<span><br/></span>General Admission - festival atmosphere, live music, food, beverages, and summer energy.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>🏖️ <span class=\"BoldText\">Flip Flop Gala</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">One of the most anticipated social events of the festival.</span><span><br/></span>10 tickets to the Flip Flop Gala - Monday, June 29<span><br/></span>A high‑energy beach party meets cocktail experience, featuring great food, drinks, music, and a relaxed Okanagan vibe<span><br/></span>An ideal setting for client entertainment or team celebration<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Added Value</span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Friend of Touchdown Kelowna Recognition</span></span><span><br/></span>Corporate purchasers will receive official onsite recognition as a “Friend of Touchdown Kelowna.”<span><br/></span>This acknowledgement celebrates your organization’s early commitment to the festival and adds an extra layer of prestige to your participation.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Package Value</span></h2><ul><li>Stated value: Over $5,500</li><li>Package price: $4,999 + GST</li></ul><span><br/></span>This represents significant added value, particularly given the sold‑out status of the BC Lions games and the limited availability of remaining inventory.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Corporate Package*  $5248.95</span>  ($4999.00 base price + $249.95 GST)<span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Corporate Packages</span> and their applicable taxes are non-refundable.</span>
""";
