	<table class=\" BorderOn\">
		<tr>
			<td align=\"left\" colspan=\"1\"><img src=\"https://system.spektrix.com/kelownacommunitytheatre/files/fbbca63c-4405-427a-b796-bfdb73167b6f.jpg\" /> </td><td align=\"left\"><h2>The Village Dance Academy presents </h2><h1><span class=\"UnderlineText\">MOMENTUM</span></h1></td>
		</tr>
	</table><span><br/></span>MOMENTUM is The Village Dance Academy’s year-end showcase celebrating the passion, dedication, and talent of Kelowna’s youth. Featuring dancers ages 2 through adult, this high-energy production highlights performances in ballet, jazz, lyrical, tap, hip hop, contemporary, and acro. Join us for an inspiring evening that showcases the heart of our community and the incredible momentum our dancers have built all season long!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2>Pricing</h2><span class=\"BoldText\">Adult  $42.61</span>  ($35.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $5.25 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Senior (65+)  $40.31</span>  ($33.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.95 service charge)<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Student w/ID  $40.31</span>  ($33.00 base price + $2.36 CIF + $4.95 service charge)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All above prices are in CAD and include GST.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>---<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Kelowna Community Theatre event tickets include a $2.36 Capital Improvement Fee (CIF). A service fee is added for box office costs, card processing, and taxes. <span class=\"BoldText\">MOMENTUM</span> tickets and their applicable service fees are non-refundable.</span>
""";
